{"tid":344416,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"剛承諾聆聽反對聲音　蔡若蓮被揭上FB即block港語學召集人","createTime":"2017-08-02T09:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T14:26:28.000Z","uid":53379,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6315933202779990b34244eac83b3a035d962db","tid":344416,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">剛承諾聆聽反對聲音　蔡若蓮被揭上FB即block港語學召集人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/choi-13_mpA4h_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchoi-13_mpA4h_1200x0.png&h=27509f71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任命備受爭議的教育局副局長蔡若蓮今天首日上班，並向傳媒承諾會細心聆聽反對聲音。不過港語學召集人陳樂行稱，其Facebook帳戶今日被蔡若蓮封鎖（block）。他質疑蔡若蓮所謂聆聽意見實屬謊言，質疑她誠信及人格何在。<br />\n<br />\n今日港語學透過Facebook發文，稱召集人陳樂行FB已被蔡若蓮封鎖，「信誓旦旦『虛心聆聽不同意見，希望社會給予時間、空間及機會』嘅教育局次長蔡若蓮，上任頭等大事竟然係趁返工時間玩facebook，封鎖港語學召集人陳樂行。可見佢以副局長身份同全港市民講嘅第一句說話，即屬謊言。誠信何在？人格何在？」<br />\n<br />\n教育局發言人回應指，蔡若蓮今日首日履新，現正考慮設立一個facebook帳戶或專頁，透過社交媒體加強與各界的聯繫和溝通，「至於其原有的個人facebook帳戶，主要是與親友作生活交流之用，不會用於現時工作相關職務。」<br />\n<br />\n一向反對普教中的港語學召集人陳樂行，上月剛與香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒等人召開記者會，反對蔡若蓮任教育局副局長一職。<br />\n<br />\n蔡若蓮今日首日上班，與教育局局長楊潤雄一同見傳媒。她稱自己主要責任支援局長，會細心聆聽反對聲音，思考背後原因，「希望大家根據我實際工作作出評論 &hellip; 香港是多元化社會，我完全明白有不同聲音。我相信，用我工作表現可釋除其他疑慮。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/剛承諾聆聽反對聲音-蔡若蓮被揭上fb即block港語學召集人/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%89%9B%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E8%81%86%E8%81%BD%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%81%B2%E9%9F%B3-%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%A5%E8%93%AE%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E4%B8%8Afb%E5%8D%B3block%E6%B8%AF%E8%AA%9E%E5%AD%B8%E5%8F%AC%E9%9B%86%E4%BA%BA%2F&d=6WmxET84T66MIiAJCCKhS%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=76c59b52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%89%9B%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E8%81%86%E8%81%BD%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%81%B2%E9%9F%B3-%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%A5%E8%93%AE%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E4%B8%8Afb%E5%8D%B3block%E6%B8%AF%E8%AA%9E%E5%AD%B8%E5%8F%AC%E9%9B%86%E4%BA%BA%2F&h=383643ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/剛承諾聆聽反對聲音-蔡若蓮被揭上fb即block港語學召集人/</a>"},{"pid":"77d575c59ddbb387f7bcb87213d6eac38be73371","tid":344416,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:14:08.000Z","msg":"港共爪牙都信佢啲承諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港只剩番一條路"},{"pid":"e14ce1969f3676fb833dad07f82ada6412cd683e","tid":344416,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7334734b651381a82e5ad1152d77768cc2e58a0","tid":344416,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc41705e5c76c72697f6ac406a0656c4711bf7d","tid":344416,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c65f1214a908f16826c0ffa986871a1a279215","tid":344416,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:20:37.000Z","msg":"根本黨委書記黎<br />\n<br />\n信佢一成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f5cdf1ab13d4b53015cef4cb92531e3588d8dc","tid":344416,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:21:44.000Z","msg":"乜仲會有人信呢一個政府官員說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b11aae9088689a012aae0f7d1b8459f06275a3","tid":344416,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}